# Firebase config files — downloaded from Firebase Console per
# environment. Mirror them in EAS Secrets (or commit *.example variants)
# so the build pipeline can drop them in at build time without leaking
# the project_id / app_id pair into the public repo.
google-services.json
GoogleService-Info.plist
